    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, your mystical touch can mend wounds. As an action, you can spend 1 @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.imsZ2GYUPlwCQqqy]{ki point} to touch a creature and restore a number of hit points equal to a roll of your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.TMeKDQLocSb3loVv]{Martial Arts} die + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<p>When you use your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.nDupigAtTVJsOVXS]{Flurry of Blows}, you can replace one of the unarmed strikes with a use of this feature without spending a ki point for the healing.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: After adding this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Ki</em></p>\n</section>",
